data.description: Newly renovated 4 bedroom house near the end of a dead end street in a charming Gales Ferry neighborhood. House has 3 bedrooms and full bath on main level along with kitchen and main living space. 2nd floor is large primary bedroom with full bath and walk out balcony overlooking wooden lot and rolling brook. Just a few miles from SubBase, close to parks and orchards. All new carpet and flooring on first floor, HVAC system currently in process of being replaced and will be completed prior to closing.
